Basic XPath Pattern
//tag_name[@attribute='value']

// → search anywhere in the document
tag_name → HTML tag name (input, div, span, table, etc.)
@attribute → attribute name (id, class, aria-label, role, data-*, etc.)
'value' → the attribute’s value (quoted)
